        {"title": "发送带参数的GET请求", "description": "编写Python代码，发送GET请求到 https://httpbin.org/get ，携带查询参数 name=test 和 age=25，并打印响应。", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "Python requests库", "knowledge_point": "GET请求参数", "code_template": "import requests\n\ndef solution():\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"GET /get?name=test&age=25\", \"expected\": \"args contains name and age\"}]", "solution": "import requests\n\ndef solution():\n    params = {'name': 'test', 'age': 25}\n    response = requests.get('https://httpbin.org/get', params=params)\n    print(response.status_code)\n    print(response.json())", "hint": "使用params字典传递查询参数"},
